# Load the flake devShell into the working environment so editors / LSP
# (rust-analyzer) and tooling resolve from the pinned toolchain.
#
# Vanilla direnv ships `use flake`. For faster, cached reloads, install
# nix-direnv (https://github.com/nix-community/nix-direnv) and it will be
# picked up automatically via your global ~/.config/direnv/direnvrc.
use flake
